      <title>特朗普监管有助于银行整合：鲍勃·戴蒙德</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-13/trump-regulation-to-aid-bank-consolidation-bob-diamond-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Atlas Merchant Capital 创始合伙人兼首席执行官 Bob Diamond 认为，美国银行整合“非常具有建设性”，将在未来三年内将金融机构数量减少到“1,000 至 2,000 家之间”，并分析了特朗普政府下预期的监管环境。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-13/trump-regulation-to-aid-bank-consolidation-bob-diamond-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 14:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加州 10 亿美元保险公司救助计划加剧住房压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/california-wildfire-insurance-losses-deepen-housing-market-strains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州的房地产市场已经是美国最昂贵的市场之一。旧金山一套公寓的价格可能与德克萨斯州一套四居室的房子一样贵，许多家庭要驱车数小时前往内陆才能找到一套第一套住房。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/california-wildfire-insurance-losses-deepen-housing-market-strains</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔债券投资者因担心选举后“混乱”而撤退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/ecuador-bond-investors-retreat-for-fear-of-post-election-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几周前，投资者纷纷购买厄瓜多尔的美元债券，因为他们看到民意调查显示，亲市场的现任总统丹尼尔·诺沃亚 (Daniel Noboa) 将在第一轮选举中获胜。随后，路易莎·冈萨雷斯 (Luisa González) 胜出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/ecuador-bond-investors-retreat-for-fear-of-post-election-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 13:57:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称将于周四下午 1 点宣布对等关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-promises-reciprocal-tariffs-today-without-giving-details</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将于周四宣布征收对等关税，并承诺兑现他的威胁，对那些对美国商品征收更高关税的国家的进口产品征收关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-promises-reciprocal-tariffs-today-without-giving-details</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 12:13:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟法院就现金贷款作出裁决 波兰银行面临新负担</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/polish-banks-face-costly-claims-as-eu-court-rules-on-cash-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧盟最高法院在有关消费贷款利息支付的纠纷中站在了客户一边，从阿利尔银行 (Alior Bank SA) 到千禧银行 (Bank Millennium SA) 等波兰银行面临新一轮诉讼，可能使该行业损失数十亿兹罗提。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/polish-banks-face-costly-claims-as-eu-court-rules-on-cash-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 09:19:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Neste 因亏损和取消股息政策而跌至 2016 年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/neste-plans-to-cut-600-jobs-cancels-dividend-in-turnaround-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芬兰可再生燃料生产商 Neste Oyj 公布第四季度亏损、取消股息政策并表示将裁员约 600 人后，其股价跌至 2016 年以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/neste-plans-to-cut-600-jobs-cancels-dividend-in-turnaround-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 08:47:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾伯塔基金关闭新加坡和纽约办事处；两名高管离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/alberta-fund-shuts-singapore-new-york-offices-two-senior-executives-leave</link>
      <description><![CDATA[艾伯塔投资管理公司 (Alberta Investment Management Corp.) 已决定关闭其在新加坡和纽约的新办事处，以缩减其全球扩张计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/alberta-fund-shuts-singapore-new-york-offices-two-senior-executives-leave</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 03:11:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰谈判前景不佳 油价跌至 12 月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统特朗普和俄罗斯总统普京同意就结束乌克兰战争进行谈判后，油价连续第二天下跌，引发市场猜测莫斯科的供应障碍可能会减轻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 23:35:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：PCE 数据向好，股市略有缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科技股上涨支撑了股市，债券收益率下降，在关键要素暗示美联储青睐的价格指标不会像人们担心的那么糟糕之后，交易员们忽略了火热的通胀数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 22:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
